attr.title: Temple of Kashteki
attr.desc:
A short platformer where the player upgrades the environment!
Escape the Temple of Kashteki!
Made for the Pursuing Pixels James Jam Game Gam
attr.inst:
Download the kashteki_linux.zip from: https://securas.itch.io/temple-of-kashteki.
Unzip and place kashteki_linux.x86_64 into ports/templeofkashteki/gamedata.
